ðŸ”¹ Strings & Algorithms

7ï¸âƒ£ Write a script to reverse a string without using built-in functions.
--->
a = 'this is jerry'
rev = ''
for i in a:
    rev = i + rev
print(rev)

8ï¸âƒ£ a = "This is Jerry" â†’ Find the concurrency (word frequency/count).
--->
a = "hello world"
for ch in set(a):
    if ch != " ":
        print(ch, ":", a.count(ch))

