ðŸ”¹ Extra Tricky Ones (commonly asked)

9ï¸âƒ£ Write a Python script to check if a given string is a palindrome.
--->
s = "madam"
rev = ""

for ch in s:
    rev = ch + rev

if s == rev:
    print("Palindrome")
else:
    print("Not Palindrome")

